Go into the **categories** view template.

<span class="filename">categories.tmpl.html</span>
```php
<h1 ng-click="setCurrentCategory(null)">Eggly</h1>
<ul class="category-list">
  <li ng-repeat="category in categories" ng-class="{'active': isCurrentCategory(category)}">
    <a ui-sref="eggly.categories.bookmarks({category:category.name})" ng-click="setCurrentCategory(category)">{{category.name}}</a>
  </li>
